de.ntcomputer.minecraft.controllablemobs.api.ai

Enum AIType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AIType>
      • de.ntcomputer.minecraft.controllablemobs.api.ai.AIType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<AIType>

    public enum AIType
extends Enum<AIType>
    An enum that lists all AI components built into the minecraft server core.
    You can use it to specifically remove default AI parts by ControllableMobAI.remove(AIType...) or ControllableMobAI.removeExcept(AIType...).
    It can be also used to identify AI parts on your own by using AIPart.getType().
    Version:
    v4
    Author:
    Cybran
